overview: A wild celebrity sex tape has leaked and it’s starring ex-sexy star Ginger Paloma. Now living in a destitute tenement with two kids, it’s finally her second wind at fame and fortune - until the real star of the sex video comes out. Majesty Zamora is younger and fresher, and she’s here to claim the fame that’s rightfully hers. Not willing to let go of this new life, Ginger gets a brilliant idea.She makes a new sex tape.
title: Boldstar
